config:
  theme: neutral
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Браузер (Next.js)
    participant API as Django API
    participant RD as Redis (брокер)
    participant CT as Celery Worker

    Note over C,CT: Инициация импорта

    C->>API: POST /api/v1/agencies/{pk}/tours/import/<br/>multipart/form-data: file=tours.csv
    API->>API: Проверка прав (IsApprovedOperator)<br/>Чтение CSV в память
    API->>RD: tour_bulk_import_task.delay(<br/>  agency_id, employee_id,<br/>  csv_text, requester_id)
    API-->>C: 202 Accepted

    Note over C,CT: Асинхронная обработка

    CT->>RD: Извлечение задачи из очереди
    CT->>CT: Agency.objects.get(...)<br/>AgencyEmployee.objects.get(...)
    CT->>CT: tour_bulk_import(agency, created_by, file)<br/>↳ построчный разбор CSV<br/>↳ Tour.objects.create(...) × N

    Note over C,CT: Уведомление о завершении

    CT->>CT: Notification.objects.create(...)<br/>{"created": N, "errors": [...]}
    CT->>RD: channel_layer.group_send(<br/>  "notifications_user_{pk}")
    RD-->>C: {"type": "notification",<br/>"message": "N tour(s) imported"}
